Version: 1.7
Release: 2%{?dist}
Summary: Set of ABI analysis tools

License: LGPLv3+
URL: https://sourceware.org/libabigail/
Source0: http://mirrors.kernel.org/sourceware/libabigail/%{tarball_name}.tar.gz

BuildRequires: gcc-c++
BuildRequires: libtool
BuildRequires: elfutils-devel
